ngineering issues and address national development issues<\/li>\n<li><strong>Rules and Regulations<\/strong>: Through the compulsory implementation of rules and regulations, enhance management and leadership skills of faculty, staffs and students, make optimum use of resources and infrastructures<\/li>\n<li><strong>Resource Planning<\/strong>: Through the resource planning and fund management obtain financial sustainability of the campus<\/li>\n<li><strong>Technology Transfer<\/strong>: Through the international collaboration and joint programs, enhance mechanisms for technology transfer and capacity building<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Vision The vision of the Pulchowk Campus is to be a premier engineering education institution at par with world-class role models. &nbsp; The Mission The Mission of Pulchowk Campus is to provide quality engineering education and research in the frontier engineering areas relevant primarily to the nation. &nbsp; Goals Pulchowk Campus has the following [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":17,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3146"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3146"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3146\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3147,"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3146\/revisions\/3147"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/pcampus.edu.np\/wp-json\/wp\